videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale shows off how to run the fast break, ending with the perfect bounce pass to Lindsay Allen as Notre Dame tries to get back into the game against UConn.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale runs Notre Dame fast break to perfection
Brianna Turner protects the rim for Notre Dame with a block on Gabby Williams

videos.description: Q2 (3:22) ND Mychal Johnson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Brianna Turner.
videos.headline: Notre Dame 3-Pointer gives them the lead over UConn

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson puts a stop to Notre Dame's momentum with the steal and goes the other way for the lay up to even the game at 34.
videos.headline: Samuelson does it all with steal and layup

videos.description: Notre Dame head coach Muffet McGraw talks about bouncing back from Notre Dame's slow offensive start
videos.headline: Notre Dame head coach Muffet McGraw talks about bouncing back from Notre Dame's slow offensive start

videos.description: Q3 (9:27) CONN Napheesa Collier made Layup. Assisted by Saniya Chong.
videos.headline: Saniya Chong's pass splits two defenders to assist a Napheesa Collier lay-up

videos.description: UConn goes from one end of the court to the other in a hurry when Gabby Williams makes the seal and instantly finds Kia Nurse down court for the easy layup.
videos.headline: UConn goes from defense to offense in a flash

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson makes the tough layup in the lane, and on the next possession Gabby Williams makes the steal and goes in for a layup of her own to boost UConn's lead.
videos.headline: Back-to-back layups has UConn running

videos.description: Q4 (9:25) ND Lindsay Allen made Layup.
videos.headline: Lindsay Allen scores on a nice move to the basket

videos.description: Q4 (3:07) CONN Katie Lou Samuelson made Layup.
videos.headline: Katie Lou Samuelson makes the and-one lay-up to give UConn a 10 point lead

videos.description: UConn guard Gabby Williams and head coach Geno Auriemma talk about how it feels to get the 72-61 victory over Notre Dame
videos.headline: UConn guard Gabby Williams and head coach Geno Auriemma talk about how it feels to get the 72-61 victory over Notre Dame

videos.description: Doris Burke and Dave O'Brien break down UConn's 72-61 victory over Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Gabby Williams comes up big for UConn against Notre Dame
